name: 無為 (Wu Wei)
description: 無為($WUWEI) is a community-driven memecoin operating on the BSC chain, established with principles of maximal transparency and security. This token was deployed as a 100% Fair Launch, no presale, no team allocation, and all tokens were immediately made fully circulating upon launch. Key security and integrity features include: 1. Full Renunciation of Contract Ownership: The contract ownership has been permanently renounced, preventing any future modification to the contract, minting of new tokens, or adjustment of transaction taxes. 2. Permanent Liquidity Lock: The initial liquidity pool (LP) tokens were permanently Burned, ensuring perpetual tradability. 3. Zero Taxes: Transactions are governed by a 0% buy and 0% sell tax structure, promoting free and high-volume trading. The project is now entirely driven by community, focusing on organic social growth and brand building based on the WuWei(or Doing Nothing) narrative. The primary function of $WUWEI is purely for entertainment and social currency.
